abstract: Who will get to control .music Internet domain has not been settled; rather, it has become the latest example of the music world's struggle over the Internet, as industry groups and technology giants like Google and Amazon compete to control the .music domain.

headline.main: Plans for a New .Music Suffix, but Who Will Own It?
